item.title: CVE-2022-33314|2024-08-03T08:01:20.596Z -- robustel -- r1510
item.description: Multiple command injection vulnerabilities exist in the web_server action endpoints functionalities of Robustel R1510 3.3.0. A specially-crafted network request can lead to arbitrary command execution. An attacker can send a sequence of requests to trigger these vulnerabilities.The `/action/import_sdk_file/` API is affected by command injection vulnerability.
